Node.Description: Go to Procurement and sourcing > Vendors > All vendors.
In the list, find and select the desired record.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
On the Action Pane, click Vendor.
Click On hold to open the drop dialog.
In the Vendor hold field, select an option.
In the Reason code field, enter or select a value.
In the list, select row 4.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
Click OK.
Click the form caption.
Close the page.
Go to Procurement and sourcing > Purchase orders > All purchase orders.
Click New.
In the Vendor account field, enter or select a value.
In the list, select row 10.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
Click OK.
Click Save.
Click the form caption.
